Without a log, it would be hard to tell what might be happening.  I don't have a fix, but a work around.  ShipManifest will allow you to change the profession of your Kerbals.  Likely not what you are looking for, but might be a short term solution while you determine the root cause.
Here's the log from my latest play session: https://file.io/ffxaUFuLCcXU
